.Dd April 23, 2026
.Dt MAT_HELP 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm Mat_Help
.Nd Prints help text and exits successfully.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Fd #include <matio.h>
.Ft void
.Fo Mat_Help
.Fa "const char *helpstr[]"
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn Mat_Help
function writes each non-NULL string from
.Fa helpstr
to standard output, one line per entry, and then exits the process with
success status.
The final array element must be NULL.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr Mat_Error 3